data.description: Welcome Home to the heart of Black Forest!  This unique property sits on 4.77 acres with dead-on views of Pikes Peak!  There are 103 living trees on the property, and the lot has perfect drainage with water run-off adjacent to the property that actually functions as running water during rainy season!  The home is just steps from the local Farmers Market and all the wonderful amenities that Black Forest has to offer.  This lot is fully fenced, including a stunning front gate that makes a dramatic first impression.  The property has an oversized three car detached garage, two storage sheds, and a huge circular roundabout driveway that make this lot truly one-of-a-kind.  The Septic System is less than a year old, and the property is in the unincorporated section of Black Forest- which is very powerful for STR opportunities.    The home itself has a unique and powerful floorplan that features 4 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms.  The unique functionality comes with the two separate entrances- which would allow for this home to be easily broken up into two very livable units that would both feature 2 beds and 2 baths.  The upper unit is ready to go- with about 1900 square feet, newer carpet, GORGEOUS tile flooring that has been installed recently, and stunning tongue-in-groove ceilings and wall finishes in the area that features the Peak views.  The lower level also has a fireplace, and Kitchen space, with a very easy layout to be finished and turned into value right away.  This is a wonderful opportunity in Black Forest- come check it out and be wowed!
